snippet.title: Tannenberg: Latvian Expansion Trailer 2019
snippet.description:
Gather under the Latvian Flag in WW1 FPS Tannenberg on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/633460

A new Latvian Riflemen squad and a swampy new Baltic map are out now in the free Latvian Expansion, plus new guns and special grenades. Check out the trailer to get a look at the Baltic map and see the new smoke and gas grenades in action...

#WW1 #WorldWarI #Tannenberg
